instruction:
Lambdas are inline function implementations. They implement functional interfaces:

```java
// Old way:
Comparator<String> c = new Comparator<String>() {
    public int compare(String a, String b) { return a.compareTo(b); }
};

// Lambda way:
Comparator<String> c = (a, b) -> a.compareTo(b);
```

Run this — lambdas replacing anonymous classes.

